100%E8%90%AC%E8%8B%B1%E9%8E%8A&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnSlkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=45178b2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/615376/英外相宣布削95-對華援助-至每年不到100萬英鎊</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:50:28.000Z","msg":"自古以來中國都係靠歐美日等發達國家援助啦<br />\n2008年以前中國人全部疫苗都係美國日本歐盟援助, 最後全部配方俾埋中國, 點知就搞啲毒疫苗、假疫苗出黎。<br />\n今時今日中國仲扮發展中國家, 收人地援助, 轉個頭就搞亂世界, 一早全世界都應該CUT哂啲援助。<br />\n香港人都年捐幾百億幫中國, 轉個頭就俾佢食碗面反碗底"},{"pid":"716d15df7f25db92e14406175ee66de8bc1ea85c","tid":2499491,"uid":119756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:50:32.000Z","msg":"脫咗貧，點解要幫，英國仲有窮人"},{"pid":"599039592a35453523e3b6fb8cb8f8c79430e4ba","tid":2499491,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:50:43.000Z","msg":"仲援咩鬼助<br />\n學日本咁cut哂佢la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b15cbec32dd8f9dfd4bc4d0b140a2ec546437b5","tid":2499491,"uid":246646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:51:20.000Z","msg":"收洋錢?! 辱華確認"},{"pid":"96e4e1fd6dc2660a16626b4dd5def33f8aeffa54","tid":2499491,"uid":10647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:52:52.000Z","msg":"世界第二經濟體aka全面脫貧國洗撚你日落國援助呀<br />\n曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89595094c0f4ff7d1afb273c2892753f76c8df9c","tid":2499491,"uid":177734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"25a6837830564248c5ef7f085930a21b3fdaaa93","tid":2499491,"uid":8014,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:32:27.000Z","msg":"世界第二大經濟體 仲要全國0貧窮人口<br />\n<br />\n點解仲要援助？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T02:53:14.000Z"